ging their fallen heroes.","genre_ids":[28,18,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.5481,"vote_count":462,"poster_path":"/yNySAgpAnWmPpYinim9E0tUzJWG.jpg","release_date":"2019-01-11","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/gEDzACsdPbsHZQ0I80FLYFCf2nt.jpg","original_title":"Uri: The Surgical Strike","original_language":"hi"},{"id":15657,"adult":false,"title":"Tarzan II","video":false,"overview":"When one of his missteps puts his family in jeopardy, Tarzan decides they would be better off without him.","genre_ids":[12,16,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.381,"vote_count":1222,"poster_path":"/dI0ANmiLaqUuBrX4v8V3ZywkyZ0.jpg","release_date":"2005-06-13","vote_average":6.087,"backdrop_path":"/lBmemfERELoZDxyLOCoumfkHAEO.jpg","original_title":"Tarzan II","original_language":"en"},{"id":575322,"adult":false,"title":"Project Gemini","video":false,"overview":"After depleting Earth's resources for centuries, humankind's survival requires an exodus to outer space. An international expedition is quickly formed to find a suitable new planet, but when plans go awry, the crew is suddenly stranded without power on a strange planet, where something unimaginable lies in wait.","genre_ids":[878,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.7126,"vote_count":487,"poster_path":"/rFljUdOozFEv6HDHIFpFvcYW0ec.jpg","release_date":"2022-01-06","vote_average":5.677,"backdrop_path":"/etP5jwlwvkNhwe7jnI2AyA6ZKrR.jpg","original_title":"Звёздный разум","original_language":"en"},{"id":790142,"adult":false,"title":"The Royal Treatment","video":false,"overview":"Isabella runs her own salon and isn’t afraid to speak her mind, while Prince Thomas runs his own country and is about to marry for duty rather than love. When Izzy and her fellow stylists get the opportunity of a lifetime to do the hair for the royal wedding, she and Prince Thomas learn that taking control of their own destiny requires following their hearts.","genre_ids":[10749,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2359,"vote_count":79