anboy of a supervillain supergroup known as the Vicious 6, Gru hatches a plan to become evil enough to join them, with the backup of his followers, the Minions.","genre_ids":[10751,35,12,16,878,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.628,"vote_count":3938,"poster_path":"/wKiOkZTN9lUUUNZLmtnwubZYONg.jpg","release_date":"2022-06-29","vote_average":7.276,"backdrop_path":"/wZS4xSfPtk1NPQnx9zsT5R2WhCu.jpg","original_title":"Minions: The Rise of Gru","original_language":"en"},{"id":111,"adult":false,"title":"Scarface","video":false,"overview":"After getting a green card in exchange for assassinating a Cuban government official, Tony Montana stakes a claim on the drug trade in Miami. Viciously murdering anyone who stands in his way, Tony eventually becomes the biggest drug lord in the state, controlling nearly all the cocaine that comes through Miami. But increased pressure from the police, wars with Colombian drug cartels and his own drug-fueled paranoia serve to fuel the flames of his eventual downfall.","genre_ids":[28,80,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.3789,"vote_count":12757,"poster_path":"/iQ5ztdjvteGeboxtmRdXEChJOHh.jpg","release_date":"1983-12-09","vote_average":8.155,"backdrop_path":"/1qM2BYNE11Viby8ImC9LC00DgDr.jpg","original_title":"Scarface","original_language":"en"},{"id":568124,"adult":false,"title":"Encanto","video":false,"overview":"The tale of an extraordinary family, the Madrigals, who live hidden in the mountains of Colombia, in a magical house, in a vibrant town, in a wondrous, charmed place called an Encanto. The magic of the Encanto has blessed every child in the family—every child except one, Mirabel. But when she discovers that the magic surrounding the Encanto is in danger, Mirabel decides that she, the only ordinary Madrigal, might just be her exceptional family's last hope.","genre_ids":[16,35,10751,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":11.8893,"vote_count":10067,"poster_path":"/4j0PNHkMr5ax3IA8tjtxcmPU3QT.jpg","release_date":"2021-10-13