9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Amor Bandido | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"Joan is a naïve, 16-year-old who falls in love easily. One day he decides to escape to the provinces with Luciana, a beautiful 35-year-old woman and a teacher at his school, in order to give free rein to his love. Soon, Joan discovers with horror that he has fallen into a trap that is a mix between sex, money, politics and violence."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/148592/amor-bandido"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"Amor Bandido"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"Joan is a naïve, 16-year-old who falls in love easily. One day he decides to escape to the provinces with Luciana, a beautiful 35-year-old woman and a teacher at his school, in order to give free rein to his love. Soon, Joan discovers with horror that he has fallen into a trap that is a mix between sex, money, politics and violence."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/148592/amor-bandido"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qb3YySysqo8ikQoagBIz29BZOmi.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Amor Bandido"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"Joan is a naïve, 16-year-old who falls in love easily. One day he decides to escape to the provinces with Luciana, a beautiful 35-year-old woman and a teacher at his school, in order to give free rein to his love. Soon, Joan discovers with horror that he has fallen into a trap that is a mix between